              "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "k3d0u",
              "name": "bP2",
              "fill": "#3D3D3D",
              "content": "We worked on many large, experiential campaigns for clients like Nike, Nintendo, Bacardi and BMW. Along with a data visualization tool to demonstrate how far a beamer could travel on a tank of diesel, we also built a BMW car configurator.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "3vPFh",
              "name": "bP3",
              "fill": "#3D3D3D",
              "content": "Once the car is set to your liking, the configuration will be sent to a database to find an appropriate dealer if the car exists or a manufacturer if it needs to be built.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
